OL,3,CMeet the 92-year-old having lunch at
OL,4,Cthe same hotel every week for 37 years
OL,6,FITV Border reporter Matthew Taylor
OL,7,Fcaught up with Molly Robinson as she
OL,8,Fenjoyed her weekly lunch at Langley
OL,9,FCastle
OL,11,FMolly Robinson has been enjoying the
OL,12,Fsame lunch at the same hotel every
OL,13,Fsingle week for almost 40 years.
OL,15,FThe 92-year-old is seen as a part of
OL,16,Fthe family at Langley Castle, near
OL,17,FHexham, in Northumberland, where she
OL,18,Fmakes the journey every Thursday from
OL,19,Fher home in Alston.
