OL,3,CMeet the 92-year-old having lunch at
OL,4,Cthe same hotel every week for 37 years
OL,6,FA lot has changed since 1987, but one
OL,7,Fthing that has remained the same is
OL,8,Fher order - soup of the day and fish
OL,9,Fand chips washed down by two glasses
OL,10,Fof Champagne.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Border, Molly said:
OL,13,F"Why wouldn't I want to come? Everyone
OL,14,Fis so friendly and nice. You don't
OL,15,Ffeel as though you are sitting amongst
OL,16,Fstrangers then. You get to know the
OL,17,Fstaff. So it is very good."
OL,19,FNow in her tenth decade, Molly no
OL,20,Flonger drives and makes her trip to
OL,21,FLangley by taxi every week.
