OL,3,CMeet the 92-year-old having lunch at
OL,4,Cthe same hotel every week for 37 years
OL,6,FShe first started visiting the castle
OL,7,Fwith her late husband Jock for
OL,8,Fovernight stays, and she continues to
OL,9,Fattend following his death.
OL,11,FAnd despite dining in the same place
OL,12,Ffor 37 years, Molly said she still
OL,13,Flooks forward to her weekly outing.
OL,15,F"Of course I do," she continued. "It
OL,16,Fis my indulgence coming here."
OL,18,F'Part of the family'
