OL,3,CMeet the 92-year-old having lunch at
OL,4,Cthe same hotel every week for 37 years
OL,6,FGeneral Manager of the hotel, Mohammed
OL,7,FSerag, told ITV Border that Molly is
OL,8,Ffar more than just a customer to
OL,9,Feveryone at Langley Castle.
OL,11,FHe said: "I have never met in my life
OL,12,Fsuch a loyal guest, she has never
OL,13,Fmissed one week, she has never missed
OL,14,Fa meal.
OL,16,F"Molly is not a guest, for us Molly is
OL,17,Fpart of the family."
